  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\n>As a user,\r\n>I want easily see what requires my attention in the Activity Center,\r\n>So that I can promptly act on the most important notifications to me.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nNowadays, notifications are sorted in status-go and status-mobile by timestamp and ID, in descending order. We need to change the implementation to put unread notifications first in the list (also ordered by timestamp and ID in descending order).\r\n\r\n### Notes\r\n\r\nIn order to sort correctly, we need to also update the reconciliation logic in status-mobile `status-im.activity_center.core/update-notifications`.\r\n",
